# Backlink Pilot — Cursor Rules

This file is a redirect. The single source of truth for AI-agent instructions
in this repo is **docs/AGENT_GUIDE.md**.

Read that file before doing anything in this repo. It covers first-time user
flow, available CLI commands and their exit-code contract, site adapters and
targets.yaml schema, operating rules, error handling, and the batch
submission playbook.

For machine-readable command metadata see agent-manifest.json.
